Dia. 01 Death in Hane
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 helps White's mistake.
\par White's hane at 2 is the vital point and Black can't live anymore.
\par \cf1\b There is death in the hane\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par After Black 3, White's connection at 4 is a good move. Next, if Black plays at A, White throws-in at B.
\par
\par }
