Dia. 02 Hane
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's tiger's mouth move at 1 is a flexible move, but White's\cf1\b  hane at 2\cf0\b0  is a \cf1\b good attack\cf0\b0  again.
\par
\par Even if Black makes an eye with 3, White's connection at 4 is a calm move and Black can't live anymore.
\par
\par A and B are miai.
\par
\par Anyway it is an important fact that if White gets to play at 2, Black is captured.
\par }
